Margalo Gillmore https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Margalo_Gillmore 0 Margaret Lorraine "Margalo" Gillmore (31 May 1897 – 30 June 1986) was an English-born American actress who had a long career as a stage actress on Broadway. She also appeared in films and TV series, mostly in the 1950s and early 1960s.
